1. High-Level Document (HLD)
High-Level Design Document for To-Do List Application

1. Overview

Project Name: To-Do List Application
Description: A web-based application that allows users to create, edit, and manage their daily tasks.
2. System Architecture

Architecture Diagram: [Include diagram here]
Key Components: Frontend (HTML, CSS, JavaScript), Backend (Node.js, Express), Database (MongoDB)
3. Key Requirements

User registration and authentication
Task creation, editing, and deletion
Task categorization and prioritization
Responsive design
4. Assumptions and Dependencies

Users have access to the internet
The application will be hosted on a cloud server
5. Constraints and Considerations

Performance should be optimized for both desktop and mobile users
Data security and privacy must be ensured
